Sparklines are mini charts which are present in mini cells of excel.

THese are mostly used to show relation b/w time and trend or for variations in dataset.


Sparklines are very small and they have limited functionality but can be used to make our user dashboard
reader friendly.

We can get this sparkline in insert section/menu of excel.Just select data and see we have 3 types of Sparklines:
1.Line : By selecting this it will draw a line chart in single chart.
2.Column : By selecting this it will draw a Column  chart in single chart.
3.Win/Loss : By selecting this it will draw a [+/-] chart in single chart.


